index=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mld1665702834457.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mld1665702834457.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mld1665702834457.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mld1665702834457\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Define Window Properties\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define the window properties for the current form.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mld1665702834457__section_w120ab1b5b1_w121ab1b5_w122ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mld1665702834457__section_w123ab1b5b3_w124ab1b5_w125ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d356791e56\">\n                       \n Fields\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4343e1_d4344e1_d4345e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dto1665702580637.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dto1665702580637.html\" title=\"Window property of a form that determines the type of window used to display the form. One of: Normal | Dialog | Primary | Secondary | Contained | Popup\">Window Type (WindowType)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4346e1_d4347e1_d4348e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kno1665702715076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.\">Caption</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4349e1_d4350e1_d4351e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecw1665702715443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.\">System Menu (SysMenu)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4352e1_d4353e1_d4354e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cwr1665702715216.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwr1665702715216.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Iconize (CanIconize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4355e1_d4356e1_d4357e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qkn1665702715286.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkn1665702715286.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Maximize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4358e1_d4359e1_d4360e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ugr1665702834531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ugr1665702834531.html\" title=\"Window property of a form component that determines whether the user can close the form window by clicking the Close button in the title bar.\">Close (CanClose) [FRM]</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4361e1_d4362e1_d4363e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjr1676877187333.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjr1676877187333.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime.\">Resizable (CanResize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4364e1_d4365e1_d4366e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ygs1665702834602.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ygs1665702834602.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether scrollbars are displayed on the form at runtime, if necessary. Valid values: True or False (default).\">No Form Scrollbars (NOFORMSCROLL)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4367e1_d4368e1_d4369e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rld1665702581999.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rld1665702581999.html\" title=\"Window property of a form that determines what happens when it loses input focus. It may be automatically closed and the Quit or Accept trigger fired , or it may stay open and be explicitly closed. Valid values: Quit or True, Accept , or False.\">Auto Close (AutoClose)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4370e1_d4371e1_d4372e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nuj1665702834673.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nuj1665702834673.html\" title=\"Specify the modality of a form, and whether it is attached or detached to its parent.\">Modality &amp; Attachment</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4373e1_d4374e1_d4375e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"azm1665702712331.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azm1665702712331.html\" title=\"Window property of a form that specifies the reading orientation of the form at runtime. If set to right-to-left, the layout and text orientation are mirrored.\">Direction</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4376e1_d4377e1_d4378e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eao1665702652656.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eao1665702652656.html\" title=\"Window property that controls whether layout information is kept. Values are True (default) or False.\">Keep Layout State (KeepLayout)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4379e1_d4380e1_d4381e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oix1665702652724.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oix1665702652724.html\" title=\"Determines how the layout state for forms and grid widgets is stored. Valid values are PROCESS, COMPONENT, or INSTANCE.\">Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4382e1_d4383e1_d4384e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uia1665702644018.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uia1665702644018.html\" title=\"Type of image to use as a background or icon—Glyph or File.\">Image Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4388e1_d4389e1_d4390e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4394e1_d4395e1_d4396e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4397e1_d4398e1_d4399e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4400e1_d4401e1_d4402e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4403e1_d4404e1_d4405e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4406e1_d4407e1_d4408e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsu1665702783988.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsu1665702783988.html\" title=\"Name of form instance that the current form will overlay. This ensures that the current form is only displayed over the specified parent, and disappears when focus is switches to another form instance. This property can only be set if the current form is a Contained Form or if the property Is Independent Form is false.\">Parent Form (TABPAGE)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4409e1_d4410e1_d4411e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pcn1665702834745.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pcn1665702834745.html\" title=\"Form property that determines whether the form can be moved independently of other forms, or whether it overlays another form.\">Is Independent Form</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mld1665702834457__li_d4412e1_d4413e1_d4414e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xvf1665702834817.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xvf1665702834817.html\" title=\"Form property that determines whether open forms are removed from the display when this form is run. True or False (Default).\">Hide Previous</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tnl1665702834887.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Defining Single Document Interface (SDI) Behavior</a><p>By default, Uniface forms use a Multiple Document Interface (MDI), but it is possible to set window properties to force Single Document Interface (SDI) behavior.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzn1665702834956.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Defining Popup Forms</a><p>Use the Window Type and other component instance properties to define a popup form.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529970\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529970\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Window Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Window Properties Define the window properties for the current form. Fields Window Type (WindowType) Caption System Menu (SysMenu) Iconize (CanIconize) Maximize Close (CanClose) [FRM] Resizable (CanResize) No Form Scrollbars (NOFORMSCROLL) Auto Close (AutoClose) Modality & Attachment Direction Keep Layout State (KeepLayout) Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE) Image Type Background Image (BackImage) Horizontal Alignment (Halign) Vertical Alignment ( Valign) Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Background Color (BackColor) Parent Form (TABPAGE) Is Independent Form Hide Previous Related Links Defining Single Document Interface (SDI) Behavior By default, Uniface forms use a Multiple Document Interface (MDI), but it is possible to set window properties to force Single Document Interface (SDI) behavior. Defining Popup Forms Use the Window Type and other component instance properties to define a popup form. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}